    generate output graphs

    fm_generate_graphs.Rd

    generate output graphs

    fm_generate_graphs(fm_model_results)

    Arguments

    fm_model_results

    list Named list obtained from `fm_fit_model()`

    Value

    list A named list of all generated graphs (step 3)

    Examples

    # \donttest{

# loading `fm_fit_model()` outputs
fm_fit_model_outputs <- readr::read_rds(
  system.file("examples", "part2_output_small.rds",
              package = "FishMap")
  )

# run function
fm_generate_graphs(fm_model_results = fm_fit_model_outputs)
#> Running step 4 -plot graphs-

#> Step 4 -plot graphs-: 0.3 sec elapsed
#> $pred_plot

#> 

# }
